	(layer "F.Cu")
	(descr "ZKNOT USB-C pigtail termination, Attestor data variant. 6 THT pads on 15mm arc centered on cable entry: D+ and D- WIRED (28AWG twisted pair), VBUS/GND 20AWG, CC1/CC2 28AWG (Rd pulldowns live on carrier). Strain relief: two 3mm half-moon cutouts flanking cable entry for zip tie + adhesive heat shrink. Origin = cable entry point (zip-tie anchor). Geometry identical to PowerVerify 4-wire arc so the same potting jig and process apply.")
